#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1086
msgid ""
"Using the component data from the <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal>, the "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Upgrade Controller</emphasis> proceeds to upgrade "
"the Edge release components in the following order:"
