#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1841 l10n/source/edge.xml:1971
msgid ""
"The user deploys the configured <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">GitRepo/Bundle</emphasis> resource to the "
"<literal>fleet-default</literal> namespace in his <literal>management "
"cluster</literal>. This is done either <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">manually</emphasis> or through the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Rancher UI</emphasis> if such is available."
