msgid ""
"Based on the above outcome it will create either a "
"<literal>os-pkg-update.service</literal> (for package updates), or a "
"<literal>os-migration.service</literal> (for migration). The service will be "
"of type <emphasis role=\"strong\">oneshot</emphasis> and will adopt the "
"following workflow:"
