#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1861
msgid ""
"Schedule a system <emphasis role=\"strong\">reboot</emphasis> so that the "
"migration can take effect"
