"Cleanup the <literal>os-pkg-update.service/os-migration.service</literal> "
"after the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\"><emphasis>systemd.service</emphasis></emphasis> has done its "
"job. It is removed from the system to ensure that no accidental "
